Package: meerkat-agent
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: ${ARCH}
Maintainer: Meerkat <meerkat@tnisoft.ro>
Depends: adduser, ca-certificates, systemd
Description: Direct monitoring agent for the Meerkat iOS app
 Meerkat Agent is a small read-only HTTPS agent installed on a VPS you own.
 It exposes system metrics and supported discovered resources for the Meerkat
 iOS app in Free/direct mode.
